---
title: Creamy Barley & Sweet Potato Risotto with Lemony Broccolini and Parmesan
description: Guess what? Most any grain can be cooked in the style of risotto for a deliciously creamy texture. Today we’re using hearty barley along with starchy sweet potato to create an ultra-silky ‘barotto.” A side of lemony, crispy broccolini is the perfect counterpoint to all that richness.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/568d731ff8b25ecf7f8b4567.jpg
